
20. **Blockchain-Based Supply Chain Traceability and Sustainability**
    - Develop a blockchain-based supply chain solution to track and verify the origin, authenticity, and sustainability of products across various industries (e.g., food, fashion, electronics).
    - Integrate IoT sensors, RFID tags, and QR codes to capture real-time data and environmental metrics throughout the supply chain.
    - Enable consumers to access transparent and immutable product information, including ethical sourcing, fair trade practices, and carbon footprint reduction efforts.